{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "c8b5d7b3-6d26-4eb4-b0b7-0d317de5c9f4",
    "name": "Time-Off Service",
    "description": "Postman collection for the current Time-Off Service implementation.\n\nImportant limitation: request creation depends on an existing local BalanceProjection row in SQLite for the same employeeId + locationId. Today there is no public HTTP endpoint to seed or refresh that local projection. Because of that, requests under the lifecycle folders assume that the local BalanceProjection was already inserted beforehand.\n\nSuggested local seed for the current phase:\n- happy flow: employeeId=emp-happy-1, locationId=loc-a, availableDays=10, reservedDays=0\n- reject flow: employeeId=emp-reject-1, locationId=loc-a, availableDays=10, reservedDays=0\n- cancel flow: employeeId=emp-cancel-1, locationId=loc-a, availableDays=10, reservedDays=0\n- hcm rejection flow: employeeId=emp-hcm-reject-1, locationId=loc-a, availableDays=10, reservedDays=0\n- retry flow: employeeId=emp-retry-1, locationId=loc-a, availableDays=10, reservedDays=0\n- insufficient local balance flow: employeeId=emp-low-1, locationId=loc-a, availableDays=1, reservedDays=0",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000"
    },
    {
      "key": "happyRequestId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "rejectRequestId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "cancelRequestId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "hcmRejectRequestId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "retryRequestId",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
